                      <div class="slide__media">      <div class="slick-media media media--image">
<img src="http://newsroom.uts.edu.au/sites/default/files/styles/wide_landscape/public/images/article_feature/file-20180303-65529-16f9wlz-%281%29.jpg?itok=yHpG4P_c" width="980" height="520" alt="The NRL?s controversial salary cap has clearly played a role in keeping the league so equal. AAP/Craig Golding" title="The NRL?s controversial salary cap has clearly played a role in keeping the league so equal. AAP/Craig Golding" /></div>
            </div>
              <div class="slide__constrained">        <div class="slide__caption">
          
                      
                          <h2 class="slide__title">The NRL?s controversial salary cap has clearly played a role in keeping the league so equal. AAP/Craig Golding</h2>
            
            
            
            
