        </div>                      
  </div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p class="uts-lead">As the 2018 NRL season kicks off, few of the game?s supporters will be aware it is enjoying a run of competitive balance unequalled anywhere in major world sport.</p>
<p>By the time of the Grand Final at the end of September, it will be more than 25 years since a team last retained the NRL crown (or that of its NSWRL/ARL predecessors).</p>
