<p><strong>What have you learnt from failure?</strong></p>
<p>"I work in start-up land, and failure is a part of every single day, and not in the sense that you're failing, but in the sense that every time you try something new, there's a chance it won't work. If you embrace that, and go out there and take that risk, you can learn from the times that things don't work, how you continue to do things better."<br /><em>Nicola Hazell, Director, <a href="https://www.shestarts.com/">SheStarts</a> </em></p>
