<img src="http://newsroom.uts.edu.au/sites/default/files/styles/wide_landscape/public/images/article_feature/The%20Perfect%20Couple%20cover%20image.jpg?itok=pQTOdNwi" width="980" height="1530" alt="Book cover for The Perfect Couple by Lexi Landsman" title="The Perfect Couple by Lexi Landsman" /></div>
