ts-lead"><em>Clanger </em>is a solo exhibition that investigates the aesthetics and spatiality of sport through data, bodies and technology.</p>
<p>Resulting from the <a href="http://www.anat.org.au/">Australian Network for Art and Technology</a>?s (ANAT) 2017 Synapse artist residency with UTS Sport and Exercise Science, Baden Pailthorpe?s <em>Clanger </em>pairs the statistical tracking of AFL player performance with the emotional intensities of the crowd.</p>
<p>The exhibition is supported through the ANAT Synapse program and UTS Sport and Exercise Science in association with the Copyright Agency?s Cultural Fund.</p>
